                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-divider"></div>
            <div class="text-center">
                <p class="footer-text mb-0">
                    <strong>DualCrop Smart Advisory System</strong> © 2024. All rights reserved. | Built with <i class="fas fa-heart" style="color: #ec4899;"></i> for Modern Agriculture
                </p>
